    <briefdescription>
<para>Controls menu visibility based on session UI focus state. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>This system monitors the session&apos;s focused entity and shows/hides menus accordingly. When the focused entity changes:<itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>The previously focused menu (if any) is hidden</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>The newly focused menu is shown along with its menu items</para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
<para>The system tracks the previous focused entity to detect focus changes and avoid redundant visibility updates.</para>
<para><simplesect kind="see"><para>MenuComponent </para>
</simplesect>
<simplesect kind="see"><para>UiFocusComponent </para>
</simplesect>
<simplesect kind="see"><para>Session::focusedEntity() </para>
</simplesect>
</para>
    </detaileddescription>
